2024 was a year of immense personal growth for me. I dedicated myself to learning and upskilling, pursuing my passion for makeup and hairstyling with professional training in Dubai. While this journey was incredibly fulfilling, it unfortunately meant I couldn’t be as active on this platform as I would have liked.

I also faced some personal challenges this year, particularly with my skin. Dealing with sensitive, acne-prone skin was tough, and it impacted my ability to create content.

But I’m entering 2025 with a renewed sense of purpose and a commitment to myself. I’ve learned so much these past years, and I’m ready to share my journey with you all. 

What you see in the above pictures and videos is my vibe, and I’m embracing it fully. It’s OUR ( my audience’s ) taste in Hairstyles, Accessories, Makeup and Outfit. 

You’ve seen me grow up creating Barbies and Princesses Content to Professional Up to date styles. I’ve allowed negativity to affect me in the past, but not anymore. I’m choosing kindness and courage, and I won’t let anything or anyone dim my light.

I’m excited for what 2025 holds, and I can’t wait to share it all with you 💜🦋
